<pb facs="#facs_560" id="279r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_560_r1l1">alſo <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ wır in <expan>ſunderh<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab>
