<ab facs="#facs_560_r1l18"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>feſt<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Natı<ex>ui</ex>tat<ex>is</ex></expan> xpı </ab>
